      • restrictionsOnTestResourceContent

        protected boolean restrictionsOnTestResourceContent()
        Are there any restrictions on the content of the resource being tested (i.e., the resource returned by CommonResourceTest.getResourceUri()). Should be true for LDP containers since PUT can't directly modify containment triples.

        This method is used for testPutReplacesResource() and testRelativeUriResolutionPut(String).

        Returns:
        true if there are restrictions on what triples are allowed; false otherwise
        See Also:
        LdpTest.restrictionsOnPostContent()
